  "description": "<p><strong>Roles & Responsibilities:</strong><br />- Bachelor degree or above, major in Finance, Computer Science, Accountancy, Business, or a quantitative discipline is a plus<br />- Possess at least 2 years of work experience<br />- Posses a strong and all-round skill set with ability to build financial models<br />- Responsible for assessing all investment and joint venture opportunities for the group<br />- Building client relationships, following up on leads, and identifying new business opportunities.<br />- Assisting with project management, planning, and improving business workflows.<br />- Conducting market research, analyzing data to identify business opportunities, and recommending improvements to business processes.<br />- Analyze financial data, identify trends, prepare reports (monthly, quarterly, annual), and provide insights to management<br />- Requires careful attention to detail<br />- Collaborating with cross-functional teams to achieve business objectives<br />- Preparing reports and presentations for management <br />- Managing communication with clients and stakeholders<br />- Be a highly motivated self-starter and a collaborative team member<br />- Able to converse in Indonesian is a plus</p>",
